data.value:
INSTRUCTIONS:
-> In the Faculty Dashboard, you can add a course you have been assigned and specify your slot preference.
-> Enter the Course Name and No. The Course Code must be unique, i.e., not added previously.
-> Specify the no. of hours of lecture, tutorials and labs per week according to the course structure.
-> Select the check boxes corresponding to the slots you prefer.
-> Click on the SUBMIT button to add the course. Please note that course once added cannot be removed.
NOTE: The slot preference would be considered on a first come first served basis. If your preferred slot has already been assigned to another course, you would be allotted the next empty slot.
